{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":864,"text":"Having spent 18 years as a child of the state"},{"time":5109,"text":"in children's homes and foster care,"},{"time":7415,"text":"you could say that I'm an expert on the subject,"},{"time":10463,"text":"and in being an expert, I want to let you know that"},{"time":14021,"text":"being an expert does in no way make you right"},{"time":19628,"text":"in light of the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22628,"text":"If you're in care, legally the government is your"},{"time":26816,"text":"parent, loco parentis."},{"time":30543,"text":"Margaret Thatcher was my mother. (Laughter)"},{"time":34492,"text":"Let's not talk about breastfeeding. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38141,"text":"Harry Potter was a foster child."},{"time":41279,"text":"Pip from \"Great Expectations\" was adopted;"},{"time":46319,"text":"Superman was a foster child;"},{"time":49401,"text":"Cinderella was a foster child;"},{"time":52929,"text":"Lisbeth Salander, the girl with the dragon tattoo,"},{"time":56537,"text":"was fostered and institutionalized;"},{"time":59459,"text":"Batman was orphaned;"},{"time":63834,"text":"Lyra Belacqua from Philip Pullman's \"Northern Lights\""},{"time":67532,"text":"was fostered;"},{"time":69221,"text":"Jane Eyre, adopted;"},{"time":71956,"text":"Roald Dahl's James from \"James and the Giant Peach;\""},{"time":76539,"text":"Matilda; Moses -- Moses! (Laughter)"},{"time":82051,"text":"Moses! (Laughter) --"},{"time":84498,"text":"the boys in Michael Morpurgo's \"Friend or Foe;\""},{"time":88994,"text":"Alem in Benjamin Zephaniah's \"Refugee Boy;\""},{"time":92810,"text":"Luke Skywalker --"},{"time":95394,"text":"Luke Skywalker! (Laughter) --"},{"time":98265,"text":"Oliver Twist;"},{"time":100552,"text":"Cassia in \"The Concubine of Shanghai\" by Hong Ying;"},{"time":104763,"text":"Celie in Alice Walker's \"The Color Purple.\""},{"time":108120,"text":"All of these great fictional characters, all of them"},{"time":112732,"text":"who were hurt by their condition,"},{"time":116729,"text":"all of them who spawned thousands of other books"},{"time":121377,"text":"and other films, all of them"},{"time":123832,"text":"were fostered, adopted or orphaned."},{"time":127985,"text":"It seems that writers know that the child"},{"time":133549,"text":"outside of family reflects on what family truly is"},{"time":140698,"text":"more than what it promotes itself to be."},{"time":144288,"text":"That is, they also use extraordinary skills"},{"time":149255,"text":"to deal with extraordinary situations on a daily basis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154084,"text":"How have we not made the connection?"},{"time":157606,"text":"And why have we not made the connection, between"},{"time":161644,"text":"— How has that happened? —"},{"time":163844,"text":"between these incredible characters of popular culture"},{"time":167412,"text":"and religions, and the fostered, adopted or orphaned child"},{"time":172500,"text":"in our midst? It's not our pity that they need."},{"time":177132,"text":"It's our respect."},{"time":179733,"text":"I know famous musicians,"},{"time":182350,"text":"I know actors and film stars and millionaires and novelists"},{"time":187422,"text":"and top lawyers and television executives"},{"time":190923,"text":"and magazine editors and national journalists"},{"time":193373,"text":"and dustbinmen and hairdressers, all who were"},{"time":196214,"text":"looked after children, fostered, adopted or orphaned,"},{"time":199750,"text":"and many of them grow into their adult lives"},{"time":202422,"text":"in fear of speaking of their background, as if it may"},{"time":206693,"text":"somehow weaken their standing in the foreground,"},{"time":211000,"text":"as if it were somehow Kryptonite, as if it were a time bomb"},{"time":215042,"text":"strapped on the inside. Children in care,"},{"time":219089,"text":"who've had a life in care, deserve the right"},{"time":222223,"text":"to own and live the memory of their own childhood."},{"time":228073,"text":"It is that simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230352,"text":"My own mother — and I should say this here —"},{"time":234358,"text":"she same to this country in the late '60s,"},{"time":238212,"text":"and she was, you know, she found herself pregnant,"},{"time":241977,"text":"as women did in the late '60s. You know what I mean?"},{"time":244072,"text":"They found themselves pregnant."},{"time":246021,"text":"And she sort of, she had no idea of the context"},{"time":250695,"text":"in which she'd landed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254815,"text":"In the 1960s -- I should give you some context -- in the 1960s,"},{"time":258663,"text":"if you were pregnant and you were single,"},{"time":262014,"text":"you were seen as a threat to the community."},{"time":264915,"text":"You were separated from your family by the state."},{"time":270774,"text":"You were separated from your family and placed into"},{"time":273476,"text":"mother and baby homes."},{"time":275598,"text":"You were appointed a social worker."},{"time":278739,"text":"The adoptive parents were lined up."},{"time":281129,"text":"It was the primary purpose of the social worker, the aim,"},{"time":285214,"text":"to get the woman at her most vulnerable time"},{"time":288555,"text":"in her entire life, to sign the adoption papers."},{"time":293908,"text":"So the adoption papers were signed."},{"time":295793,"text":"The mother and baby's homes were often run by nuns."},{"time":299363,"text":"The adoption papers were signed,"},{"time":302539,"text":"the child was given to the adoptive parents, and the mother"},{"time":306235,"text":"shipped back to her community"},{"time":308659,"text":"to say that she'd been on a little break."},{"time":311650,"text":"A little break."},{"time":314336,"text":"A little break."},{"time":316014,"text":"The first secret of shame for a woman"},{"time":319579,"text":"for being a woman, \"a little break.\""},{"time":324658,"text":"The adoption process took, like, a matter of months,"},{"time":327749,"text":"so it was a closed shop, you know, sealed deal,"},{"time":331629,"text":"an industrious, utilitarian solution:"},{"time":338134,"text":"the government, the farmer,"},{"time":341492,"text":"the adopting parents, the consumer,"},{"time":345339,"text":"the mother, the earth, and the child, the crop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350141,"text":"It's kind of easy to patronize the past,"},{"time":354795,"text":"to forego our responsibilities in the present."},{"time":359699,"text":"What happened then is a direct reflection"},{"time":363551,"text":"of what is happening now. Everybody believed themselves"},{"time":368795,"text":"to be doing the right thing by God and by the state"},{"time":373332,"text":"for the big society, fast-tracking adoption."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380219,"text":"So anyway, she comes here, 1967, she's pregnant,"},{"time":385412,"text":"and she comes from Ethiopia that was celebrating"},{"time":390490,"text":"its own jubilee at the time"},{"time":393188,"text":"under the Emperor Haile Selassie,"},{"time":395958,"text":"and she lands months before the Enoch Powell speech,"},{"time":401084,"text":"the \"Rivers of Blood\" speech."},{"time":403204,"text":"She lands months before the Beatles release \"The White Album,\""},{"time":407826,"text":"months before Martin Luther King was killed."},{"time":410510,"text":"It was a summer of love if you were white."},{"time":412961,"text":"If you were black, it was a summer of hate."},{"time":416653,"text":"So she goes from Oxford, she's sent to the north of England"},{"time":422303,"text":"to a mother and baby home, and appointed a social worker."},{"time":426663,"text":"It's her plan. You know, I have to say this in the Houses --"},{"time":430903,"text":"It's her plan to have me fostered for a short period of time"},{"time":435174,"text":"while she studies. But the social worker,"},{"time":438749,"text":"he had a different agenda."},{"time":441743,"text":"He found the foster parents, and he said to them,"},{"time":445950,"text":"\"Treat this as an adoption. He's yours forever."},{"time":449782,"text":"His name is Norman.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":453229,"text":"Norman! (Laughter)"},{"time":455566,"text":"Norman!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":458278,"text":"So they took me. I was a message, they said."},{"time":464504,"text":"I was a sign from God, they said."},{"time":466963,"text":"I was Norman Mark Greenwood."},{"time":470707,"text":"Now, for the next 11 years, all I know is that this woman,"},{"time":474126,"text":"this birth woman, should have her eyes scratched out"},{"time":476714,"text":"for not signing the adoption papers. She was an evil woman"},{"time":479716,"text":"too selfish to sign, so I spent those 11 years"},{"time":482793,"text":"kneeling and praying."},{"time":485549,"text":"I tried praying. I swear I tried praying."},{"time":488670,"text":"\"God, can I have a bike for Christmas?\""},{"time":492478,"text":"But I would always answer myself, \"Yes, of course you can.\""},{"time":496826,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":498440,"text":"And then I was supposed to determine whether that"},{"time":501177,"text":"was the voice of God or it was the voice of the Devil."},{"time":504709,"text":"And it turns out I've got the Devil inside of me."},{"time":512068,"text":"Who knew? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514476,"text":"So anyway, two years sort of passed,"},{"time":517372,"text":"and they had a child of their own,"},{"time":519150,"text":"and then another two years passed, and they had another child of their own,"},{"time":521614,"text":"and then another time passed"},{"time":523905,"text":"and they had another child that they called an accident,"},{"time":526482,"text":"which I thought was an unusual name. (Laughter)"},{"time":529890,"text":"And I was on the cusp of, sort of, adolescence,"},{"time":533619,"text":"so I was starting to take biscuits from the tin without asking."},{"time":538024,"text":"I was starting to stay out a little bit late, etc., etc."},{"time":541801,"text":"Now, in their religiosity, in their naivete,"},{"time":545204,"text":"my mom and dad, which I believed them to be forever,"},{"time":547641,"text":"as they said they were, my mom and dad"},{"time":550909,"text":"conceived that I had the Devil inside of me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557718,"text":"And what -- I should say this here, because this is how"},{"time":559776,"text":"they engineered my leaving."},{"time":561735,"text":"They sat me at a table, my foster mom, and she said to me,"},{"time":565124,"text":"\"You don't love us, do you?\" At 11 years old."},{"time":567192,"text":"They've had three other children. I'm the fourth. The third was an accident."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570701,"text":"And I said, \"Yeah, of course I do.\" Because you do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574746,"text":"My foster mother asked me to go away to think about love"},{"time":576897,"text":"and what it is and to read the Scriptures and to come back tomorrow"},{"time":579741,"text":"and give my most honest and truthful answer."},{"time":582684,"text":"So this was an opportunity. If they were asking me"},{"time":585524,"text":"whether I loved them or not, then I mustn't love them,"},{"time":587860,"text":"which led me to the miracle of thought that I thought they wanted me to get to."},{"time":590725,"text":"\"I will ask God for forgiveness and His light will shine"},{"time":593396,"text":"through me to them. How fantastic.\" This was an opportunity."},{"time":597164,"text":"The theology was perfect, the timing unquestionable,"},{"time":599949,"text":"and the answer as honest as a sinner could get."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602852,"text":"\"I mustn't love you,\" I said to them. \"But I will ask God for forgiveness.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":607540,"text":"\"Because you don't love us, Norman,"},{"time":610092,"text":"clearly you've chosen your path.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":612436,"text":"Twenty-four hours later, my social worker,"},{"time":615234,"text":"this strange man who used to visit me every couple of months,"},{"time":618283,"text":"he's waiting for me in the car as I say goodbye to my parents."},{"time":621495,"text":"I didn't say goodbye to anybody, not my mother, my father,"},{"time":624071,"text":"my sisters, my brothers, my aunts, my uncles,"},{"time":625899,"text":"my cousins, my grandparents, nobody."},{"time":629528,"text":"On the way to the children's home, I started to ask myself,"},{"time":633075,"text":"\"What's happened to me?\""},{"time":636050,"text":"It's not that I'd had the rug pulled from beneath me"},{"time":639203,"text":"as much as the entire floor had been taken away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644018,"text":"When I got to the —"},{"time":647818,"text":"For the next four, five years,"},{"time":652201,"text":"I was held in four different children's homes."},{"time":657054,"text":"On the third children's home, at 15,"},{"time":660331,"text":"I started to rebel, and what I did was,"},{"time":663498,"text":"I got three tins of paint, Airfix paint that you use for models,"},{"time":667827,"text":"and I was -- it was a big children's home, big Victorian children's home --"},{"time":671658,"text":"and I was in a little turret at the top of it,"},{"time":673498,"text":"and I poured them, red, yellow and green,"},{"time":676801,"text":"the colors of Africa, down the tiles."},{"time":681842,"text":"You couldn't see it from the street, because the home"},{"time":684346,"text":"was surrounded by beech trees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686798,"text":"For doing this, I was incarcerated for a year"},{"time":691754,"text":"in an assessment center which was actually"},{"time":694739,"text":"a remand center. It was a virtual prison"},{"time":699459,"text":"for young people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703357,"text":"By the way, years later, my social worker said"},{"time":705410,"text":"that I should never have been put in there."},{"time":706869,"text":"I wasn't charged for anything. I hadn't done anything wrong."},{"time":709524,"text":"But because I had no family to inquire about me,"},{"time":714250,"text":"they could do anything to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719001,"text":"I'm 17 years old, and"},{"time":722355,"text":"they had a padded cell."},{"time":725996,"text":"They would march me down corridors in last-size order."},{"time":731956,"text":"They -- I was put in a dormitory"},{"time":734221,"text":"with a confirmed Nazi sympathizer."},{"time":738141,"text":"All of the staff were ex-police -- interesting --"},{"time":741463,"text":"and ex-probation officers."},{"time":743477,"text":"The man who ran it was an ex-army officer."},{"time":747540,"text":"Every time I had a visit by a person who I did not know"},{"time":750700,"text":"who would feed me grapes, once every three months,"},{"time":754434,"text":"I was strip-searched."},{"time":756645,"text":"That home was full of young boys who were on remand"},{"time":759898,"text":"for things like murder."},{"time":765166,"text":"And this was the preparation that I was being given"},{"time":769198,"text":"after 17 years as a child of the state."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775249,"text":"I have to tell this story."},{"time":777832,"text":"I have to tell it, because there was no one"},{"time":780102,"text":"to put two and two together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":783055,"text":"I slowly became aware that I knew nobody"},{"time":786082,"text":"that knew me for longer than a year."},{"time":789576,"text":"See, that's what family does."},{"time":792425,"text":"It gives you reference points."},{"time":794816,"text":"I'm not defining a good family from a bad family."},{"time":797304,"text":"I'm just saying that you know when your birthday is"},{"time":799120,"text":"by virtue of the fact that somebody tells you when your birthday is,"},{"time":801776,"text":"a mother, a father, a sister, a brother, an aunt, an uncle,"},{"time":803723,"text":"a cousin, a grandparent. It matters to someone,"},{"time":805733,"text":"and therefore it matters to you. Understand,"},{"time":808020,"text":"I was 14 years old, tucked away in myself, into myself,"},{"time":812249,"text":"and I wasn't touched either, physically touched."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817031,"text":"I'm reporting back. I'm reporting back simply to say that"},{"time":825158,"text":"when I left the children's home I had two things"},{"time":828373,"text":"that I wanted to do. One was to find my family,"},{"time":832170,"text":"and the other was to write poetry."},{"time":833700,"text":"In creativity I saw light."},{"time":836249,"text":"In the imagination I saw the endless possibility of life,"},{"time":841411,"text":"the endless truth, the permanent creation of reality,"},{"time":847312,"text":"the place where anger was an expression"},{"time":853775,"text":"in the search for love, a place where dysfunction"},{"time":857523,"text":"is a true reaction to untruth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":862241,"text":"I've just got to say it to you all: I found all of my family"},{"time":865788,"text":"in my adult life. I spent all of my adult life finding them,"},{"time":869151,"text":"and I've now got a fully dysfunctional family just like everybody else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873166,"text":"But I'm reporting back to you to say quite simply"},{"time":876906,"text":"that you can define how strong a democracy is"},{"time":882418,"text":"by how its government treats its child."},{"time":887651,"text":"I don't mean children. I mean the child of the state."},{"time":889707,"text":"Thanks very much. It's been an honor. (Applause)"},{"time":894674,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}